{"tid":675976,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中國統戰再出新招！ 考慮對台灣人發身分證","createTime":"2018-05-24T04:05:42.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-24T05:57:21.000Z","uid":39464,"like":24,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"b2ee470a136f4eb46e5b89e67aad9ee3cf134303","tid":675976,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T04:05:42.000Z","msg":"〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕國安會前秘書長、台北論壇董事蘇起日前組團赴中國訪問，他帶回中國政府最新訊息，稱中國已經開始思考，將在中國發展的台灣人視為中國國民，考慮向他們發予中國身分證。<br />\n對台31條是否會造成台灣社會出現「離土」現象。對此，中國認為，只要台灣方面的歸路是順暢的，就不會有人聚集在中國不回去，台灣人民到中國發展就不會有「離土」的問題。如果台灣繼續實行「推出去」的政策，北京不排除考慮改變政策，改變對台灣人身分認定。<br />\n《聯合報》報導，蘇起帶回的中國政府最新訊息指出，在中國發展的台生、台師、台商，因為蔡政府懲罰的手段，讓這些台灣人「有家難歸」，中國考慮對他們發放中國身分證，視為中國國民。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://m.ltn.com.tw/news/politics/breakingnews/2435741\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fpolitics%2Fbreakingnews%2F2435741&d=24PkLJ6Ty%2FO0VFS1NGPvh1KzBYqMCiHg3GgvTcrvEuQ%3D&h=a5e06b27\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fpolitics%2Fbreakingnews%2F2435741&h=c2ca68ff\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://m.ltn.com.tw/news/politics/breakingnews/2435741</a>"},{"pid":"fe07fde4479efc7f583435de3fb3df445d38ce24","tid":675976,"uid":53026,"like":34,"dislike":0,"score":34,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T04:06:56.000Z","msg":"香港愛國人士身先士卒啦"},{"pid":"6418b1646c0ac7eca577f1594ca6d3d04ae32d2c","tid":675976,"uid":89530,"like":28,"dislike":0,"score":28,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T04:15:17.000Z","msg":"派埋俾香港啲官同議員，快啲香港試行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bbfe4cf220c5f6e6a30852e9bddaaebf91aa7274","tid":675976,"uid":2959,"like":10,"dislike":3,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T04:16:29.000Z","msg":"冇人想要<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05ce6c89186a6c17d56bc0793a4eae1cbf8c31f8","tid":675976,"uid":37757,"like":6,"dislike":6,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T04:18:02.000Z","msg":"PTT 鄉民： 回家了!"},